About this item

  • Efficient and noiseless - enjoy bullet/sonic ice cubes in just 6-8 minutes with this countertop nugget ice maker that operates quietly and swiftly.
  • High capacity - this portable ice machine produces 26 pounds of ice a day, and it stores up to 1.5 pounds of soft ice, mini size but large Ice production
  • User friendly - equipped with an intuitive LED control panel, this mini ice chip maker is easy to set up and allows you to choose between two different sizes of ice cubes. If you love to chew ice, the ice maker makes soft ice especially on the small setting
  • Safety first - the portable ice machine automatically stops making ice when the basket is full or water needs refilling, ensuring a worry-free experience
  • PORTABLE&COMPACT - The mini machine measures 9.5 x 12.9 x 14.1 inches. it's perfect for various occasions such as parties, kitchens, offices, camping trips, RVs, motorhomes or bars without taking up too much space on your counter top! The best New Year gift!

        Product Description

        SMETA Countertop Ice Maker Portable Ice Machine Compact Mini Ice Maker Machine Produce 26lbs per Day Bullet Ice Cube, Silver


        WE ARE PROFESSIONAL

        If there are any problems with the appliance, please let us know, and we will try our best to solve the problems.

        Product Details & Features

        • Material: Plastic
        • Use tap or bottled water
        • No drain pipe required

        • Daily Ice Making Capacity: 26 lb
        • Ice Shape: Bullet, make 2 different ice cube size
        • Net Weight:18 lb；Power:110V /60HZ
        • Product Dimensions:9.5*14.1*12.9 inch

        SMETA portable ice maker is the perfect appliance to keep your drinks cool on any occasion,you’ll never run out of ice when you need it.

        The Best Gift for You!

        • As we all know, bullet ice has no sharp corners and will not hurt your mouth. You can choose between large or small ice cubes.
        • Three LED indicators will let you know the working status of the machine：whether or not the ice storage basket is full, may you or may not need to add water, and if the machine is making ice.
        • The ice maker also features fast production - 9 pieces batch in just 6 to 12 minutes and up to 26 pounds of ice in 24 hours.

        • No need to drain the melted ice as it drains back to the reservoir.
        • This countertop ice machine features a compressor cooling system and operates at low noise.
        • The ice making speed depends on the selection of ice cube size and on the room temperature.

        SMETA portable ice maker

        Quick Ice Making-This countertop ice machine creates bullet shaped ice cubes; 26lbs of ice ready in 24 hours, 9 cubes made per cycle within 10 mins; you can perfectly use it for drinks, wine, smoothies, food

        SMETA Countertop ice maker

        Simple Operation-Adding the water tank with purified water; Power on machine and press "on/off" button to start ice making process; After 8-12 minutes, ice cube will fall off into the ice basket automatically

        Visualization

        Designed with compressor cooling system, operates at low noise and will not disturb your normal life; See-through window on top allows you to easily view the progress and check ice level

        Summer Complete With SMETA

        Say hello to this perfectly compact, stylish and portable appliance that will keep your beverages nice and chilled! Idea for you home, office, kitchen, bar or coffee shop. Ensuring that you have ice ready whenever you need it.

        IMPORTANT THINGS TO KNOW: If the machine has been in any other position than upright, leave it upright for 24 hours for the coolant to settle This ice maker does come with an ice scoop and ice bucket,wash the tray and scoop in warm soapy water before using For full instructions and safety warnings, always refer to packing box or the user manual

        PLEASE NOTE: Although it is well insulated, this ice machine is not a freezer. Our innovative design allows the water from the melted ice to be recycled by the machine to produce more ice. If there is any problem with the product, we will give 100% satisfied solution

        • Read the user manual thoroughly before using the ice maker.
        • After receiving the product, please let it stand upright steadily on a flat and stable for 2-4 hours before turning it on.
        • Please do not use distilled water, pure water with low TDS value, water for various beverages, warm water, water with a high PH.
        • To ensure normal use, please use running water, mineral water, conventional pure water.
        • Please do not turn the ice maker upside down or tilt it more than 45°during transportation or use. If in any case, it happens, level and let it stand upright for at least 2 hours before you plug in and use the unit again.
        • The ice maker is not a freezer. Please use the ice ASAP or transfer it to your freezer.
        • Please operate the ice maker at an environment with an ambient temperature between 10℃ and 32℃ and fill the water reservoir with water ranges between 8℃ and 28℃.
        • Please empty the water reservoir and dry it for storage if the ice maker is not used for a long time.

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        bikenerd
        5.0 out of 5 stars Produces Ice Fast
        Reviewed in the United States on February 26, 2022
        Verified Purchase
        I have to admit I was geeked out when my ice maker arrived. I spent several hours making ice for no reason and watching as the ice dropped and the mechanical scooper lifted the ice into the basket.

        I was impressed...from when you plugged the machine in and turned it on it only took 7-8 minutes to make a batch of ice. Although I was impressed I waited to review this until after I had a gathering to see how well it kept up with my guest's consumption.

        I turned the machine on about 3hrs before I had guests and the basket was full and the machine sat idle for a bit until the ice was starting to get consumed. I have to say the machine kept up very well...we never ran out of ice.

        The machine isn't silent but it isn't loud either. If you have people talking in the room you barely notice it running in the background. You will see reviews with folks whining that the ice melts while in the holding basket. The whiners aren't wrong but it doesn't matter because the machine will take the ice corpses and make more ice. Not only that the water in the reservoir will get colder and colder which will increasingly make the ice last longer.

        Bottom line...for the price, ease of operation and ease of cleaning this little gem is worth the money.

        Cheers!
